Date: 2003/1/20 16:00 
Title: HPCx changes
Author: Julian Gale <j.gale@ic.ac.uk>

Description:

A small number of changes have been made for easy compilation on an
IBM Regatta machine to enable use with the HPCx service in the UK
(and elsewhere).

